---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - CleanBoard">
    <div class="container content">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">
            Last updated: {
                new Date().toLocaleDateString("en-US", {
                    month: "long",
                    day: "numeric",
                    year: "numeric",
                })
            }
        </p>

        <section>
            <p>
                At CleanBoard, we take your privacy seriously. This policy
                explains how we handle your dataâ€”or more accurately, why we
                don't handle it at all.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h3>1. No Data Collection</h3>
            <p>
                CleanBoard is designed to be a completely offline keyboard. We
                do not collect, store, or transmit any of your personal data,
                keystrokes, or typing history. Everything you type remains on
                your device and is never sent to any external server.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h3>2. No Internet Permission</h3>
            <p>
                The CleanBoard app does not require and does not use the Android
                "Internet" permission. This means the app is technically
                incapable of sending any information from your device to the
                internet.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h3>3. Permissions Usage</h3>
            <p>
                CleanBoard may request the following permissions only for
                essential functionality:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>Vibration:</strong> To provide haptic feedback when you
                    press a key (if enabled).
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h3>4. Third-Party Services</h3>
            <p>
                CleanBoard does not use any third-party analytics, tracking, or
                advertising SDKs. There is no hidden code that monitors your
                usage.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h3>5. Policy Updates</h3>
            <p>
                We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes
                will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h3>6. Contact</h3>
            <p>
                If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you can
                contact us at: <a href="mailto:privacy@heymeowcat.is-a.dev"
                    >privacy@heymeowcat.is-a.dev</a>
            </p>
        </section>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .content {
        padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
        max-width: 700px;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .last-updated {
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
    }

    section {
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    h3 {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--foreground);
    }

    p,
    ul {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: var(--muted-foreground);
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .content {
            padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
        }
    }
</style>
